('chk-specialization-certification', 'ph-certification-specialization', 90, 'checkpoint', 'assessment', NULL, NULL, 'Specialization and Career Readiness Review', 'Review checkpoint for Certification and Specialization Tracks. The learner consolidates evidence from Cloud Engineering Specialization, Kubernetes Platform Specialization, SRE Specialization, DevSecOps Specialization, identifies unresolved prerequisite gaps, and decides whether to continue, review selected topics, or complete extra practice before the next roadmap segment.', 'checkpoint', 2, 'advanced', '{"reviewFocus":"Review checkpoint for Certification and Specialization Tracks. The learner consolidates evidence from Cloud Engineering Specialization, Kubernetes Platform Specialization, SRE Specialization, DevSecOps Specialization, identifies unresolved prerequisite gaps, and decides whether to continue, review selected topics, or complete extra practice before the next roadmap segment.","reviewCriteria":["List the roadmap items reviewed for this checkpoint.","Provide one evidence artifact such as notes, a diagram, a lab result, code, queries, screenshots, or a project review.","Record at least two gaps, risks, or follow-up actions, or explicitly state that no critical gaps were found.","Use the result to choose one next step: continue, review selected topics, or complete extra practice."],"source":"platform-generated"}'::jsonb, true, true, '["Summarize the main concepts and decisions from Certification and Specialization Tracks in practical DevOps engineering terms.", "Identify prerequisite gaps, unclear topics, or risks that should be reviewed before moving forward.", "Create a short evidence artifact that links completed roadmap items to what was learned."]'::jsonb, '["List the roadmap items reviewed for this checkpoint.", "Provide one evidence artifact such as notes, a diagram, a lab result, code, queries, screenshots, or a project review.", "Record at least two gaps, risks, or follow-up actions, or 